### Arabic

إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ يَخْشَوْنَ رَبَّهُم بِٱلْغَيْبِ لَهُم مَّغْفِرَةٌ وَأَجْرٌ كَبِيرٌ

### English

Indeed, those in awe of their Lord without seeing Him will have forgiveness and a mighty reward.